\c 97 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 97\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyo Mootii Ta'uu Isaatti Gammaduu
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo mootii dha! Lafti gammachuu haa qabaattu! Biyyi bishaan keessaa warri baay'een haa gammadan.
\m \bd 2\bd* Duumessi ifaan, duumessi gurraachi dukkanaa'aanis isatti naanna'anii jiru, teessoon isaas qajeelummaa fi dhugaa irra dhaabate.
\m \bd 3\bd* Ibiddi fuula isaa dura in adeema, diinota isaa naannoo isaatii nyaatee in fixa.
\m \bd 4\bd* balaqqeessi isaa biyya lafaa in ibsa, lafti isa in arga, in rom'as;
\m \bd 5\bd* fuula Waaqayyoo duraa, fuula gooftaa guutummaa lafaa duraa, tulloonni akka gagaa in baqu.
\m \bd 6\bd* Bantiiwwan waaqaa qajeelummaa isaa in labsu, sabni hundinuus ulfina isaa in argu.
\m \bd 7\bd* Warri bifa fakkeenyaa dhaabbatanii hojjetaniif hundinuu, waaqayyolii tolfamaniinis warri of jajan in yeellaasifamu; waaqayyoliin hundinuu gooftichaaf in sagadu.
\m \bd 8\bd* Warri Xiyoon kana dhaga'anii in gammadu, ijoolleen Yihudaas firdii kennuu keetiif in ililchu, yaa Waaqayyo!
\m \bd 9\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ati guutummaa lafaa hundumaa gararraa jirta, waaqayyolii hundumaa gararraattis ol ol in jetta.
\m \bd 10\bd* Isin warri Waaqayyoon jaallattan wanta hamaa jibbaa! Inni lubbuu warra isaaf of kennanii in eega, harka jal'ootaas isaan in oolcha.
\m \bd 11\bd* Nama qajeelaaf ifni, warra gara-qajeelotaafis gammachuun in ba'a.
\m \bd 12\bd* qajeelota nana, Waaqayyotti gammadaa, seenaa qulqullina isaatiifis galata isaaf galchaa!
